name: Fast and Furious: Urayasu (Jonathan Emerick)
description:
WELCOME TO URAYASU, JAPAN:

Take your place in the city of Urayasu by completing missions to collect cash. Use the money to tune and buy new cars.

CONTROLS:

WASD/Arrow Keys to move
Space to boost
X to enter or leave

FEEDBACK:

Click Here.

MORE INFO:
A two weeks college project based on The fast and furious franchise created by Jamie, Jonathan, and Tayler (No Sleep Inc.).
Hardware Acceleration is required for a smooth experience.
